data.description: This gorgeous brick and rock home is nestled on a 0.30+/- size lot in the prestigious Sage Meadows Subdivision situated within walking distance to the clubhouse, pool, and tennis courts. Step inside and be captivated by the grandeur of the spacious interiors, featuring high-end finishes, and designer touches throughout. Featuring 2,904 +/- square feet of well laid out living space across two stories that includes four spacious bedrooms each with oversized walk-in closets, and 3.5 baths. The main level boasts a split floor plan including three bedrooms along with two and a half baths, with the other oversized bedroom and full bath located upstairs. The master bathroom features a spa-like experience with a 5’ jet tub, a large walk-in tiled shower, and a bidet. In addition to all the pluses this house offers, a newer roof as well as gutters have also recently been installed. From the stunning architecture to the meticulously landscaped grounds, every detail has been thoughtfully curated to provide a truly exceptional living experience. Live the life of luxury at 3301 Prestwick Circle, call today to schedule your private showing before it's gone!!!
